# Dirtree: Stateful directory trees in the CLI for humans and LLMs. https://github.com/pmarreck/dirtree
ver=1.2
annotate=[
	.mechatron-prime/targets = Exact-commit Mechatron Prime CI target manifest for the runnable package and full Nix test check.
	LEARNINGS.md = environment and repo workflow learnings discovered during implementation
	MEMORIES/Bubble Tea reserves space as KeySpace so focused text input needs explicit routing = Project lesson on Bubble Tea space events and focused text-input ownership.
	MISTAKES.md = workflow mistakes observed during agent work for future avoidance
	README.md = Project overview, usage, controls, development guidance, and dynamic Mechatron Prime CI status badge.
	internal/audio/buffered_preload_test.go = regression test for completed short downloads satisfying preload
	internal/audio/hls_decoder.go = ffmpeg-backed HLS decoder that emits seekable in-memory PCM for SoundCloud streams
	internal/audio/pcm_streamer.go = seekable Beep streamer over stereo s16le PCM bytes decoded from HLS
	internal/audio/pcm_streamer_test.go = unit tests for PCM frame alignment, streaming, and seek behavior
	internal/audio/stream.go = SoundCloud stream extraction and format selection, including direct transcoding URL resolution
	internal/audio/timeouts.go = Shared playback and stream-start timeout constants.
	internal/soundcloud/client.go = SoundCloud api-v2 client for auth, library playlists/favorites, playlist hydration, and media URL resolution
	internal/soundcloud/client_test.go = fixture tests for playlists, favorites, large playlist hydration, and transcoding media URL resolution
	internal/soundcloud/live_debug_test.go = Env-gated live SoundCloud transcoding metadata debug probe with URL/key redaction.
	internal/ui/app/app.go = Coordinates TUI navigation, playback state, library views, and dynamic tab labels.
	internal/ui/components/search/search.go = Search state machine and renderer; accepts Bubble Tea KeySpace explicitly in text input.
	test = Canonical full-suite runner for the same hermetic Nix test derivation used by Mechatron Prime.
	tests/unit/audio/ffmpeg_hls_decoder_test.go = tests ffmpeg HLS command construction, PCM output, and URL-redacted errors
	tests/unit/ui/app_test.go = Exercises application navigation, playback, library, mouse, layout, and header rendering behavior.
]
